      "review_summary": "The PR adds an app-chat `pendingDraftClear` marker that drops the first same-session draft change matching the just-submitted text after send, plus app-chat tests for stale replay and different new input.\n\nPR surface: Source +17, Tests +52. Total +69 across 2 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. at source level. Current main clears the host/local draft after send, but the chat view can later commit a replayed textarea value through `onDraftChange` while the send is active; the linked issue provides browser steps for the visible symptom.",
